"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.14\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.14</span> 标题：绳、带（rope, cord）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אַגְמוֹן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’agmon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:26\">JOB 40:26</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חֶבֶל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chevel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:15\">JOS 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:2\">2SA 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:2\">2SA 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:2\">2SA 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:13\">2SA 17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:6\">2SA 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:31\">1KI 20:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:32\">1KI 20:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:8\">JOB 36:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:25\">JOB 40:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:5\">PSA 18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:6\">PSA 18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:3\">PSA 116:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:61\">PSA 119:61</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:22\">PRO 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:6\">ECC 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:18\">ISA 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:20\">ISA 33:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:23\">ISA 33:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:11\">JER 38:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:12\">JER 38:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:13\">JER 38:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:24\">EZK 27:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:4\">HOS 11:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מֵיתָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：meythar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:18\">EXO 35:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:40\">EXO 39:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:26\">NUM 3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:37\">NUM 3:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:26\">NUM 4:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:32\">NUM 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:2\">ISA 54:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:20\">JER 10:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מֹשְׁכוֹת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：moshkoth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:31\">JOB 38:31</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：נִקְפָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：niqfah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:24\">ISA 3:24</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עֲבֹת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘avoth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:14\">EXO 28:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:14\">EXO 28:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:22\">EXO 28:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:24\">EXO 28:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:25\">EXO 28:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:15\">EXO 39:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:17\">EXO 39:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:18\">EXO 39:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:13\">JDG 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">JDG 15:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:11\">JDG 16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:12\">JDG 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:10\">JOB 39:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:3\">PSA 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:27\">PSA 118:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:4\">PSA 129:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:18\">ISA 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:25\">EZK 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:8\">EZK 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:4\">HOS 11:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ζευκτηρία</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：zeuktēria)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:40\">ACT 27:40</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κλῶσμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：klōsma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir6:30\">SIR 6:30</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：νευρά</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：neura)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc7:1\">2MA 7:1</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σχοινίον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：schoinion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:15\">JHN 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:32\">ACT 27:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:43\">LJE 1:43</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0378_rope.jpg\" alt=\"绳索，可能由棕榈纤维制成（约公元前1550-1295年，新王国时期（New Kingdom），埃及，底比斯（Thebes），德拉-阿布-埃尔-纳加（Dra Abu el-Naga））\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">绳索，可能由棕榈纤维制成（约公元前1550–1295年，新王国时期（New Kingdom），埃及，底比斯（Thebes），德拉-阿布-埃尔-纳加（Dra Abu el-Naga）） (Rogers Fund, 1912, Metropolitan Museum of Art, CC0)</figcaption></figure>绳子是一条相当粗的带子，用几股线扭绕或编织而成。绳子可由多种材料制成，包括棕榈纤维、亚麻线、芦苇等。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>绳子有多种用途，例如把东西捆绑在一起，把役畜套到农具或车上，把人绑起来，甚至测量长度。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在《出埃及记》中，希伯来文<em>‘avoth</em> 指的是在以弗得和肩带之间，像绳子一样的短连接物。经文指出这些连接物是由纯金制成。学者将其解作由多个链节组成的链子，或是由金丝编织而成的绳子。各译本的译法不一，但都没能让读者真正清晰地理解（也由此反映出希伯来文本的含糊）；例如，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:14\">EXO 28:14</a> 中，“纯金拧成的链条”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 直译），“像绳一样捻成的纯金链”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译），“做成绳索样式的纯金链”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 直译），“纯金链；像编绳一样进行编绕”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> 直译）。《〈出埃及记〉手册》（<em>A Handbook on Exodus</em> ，第656页）提供的另一种翻译方式是：“他们像编绳一样编绕（或译：拧绕）的金索。”</p>\n<p>在许多语言中，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:8\">JOB 36:8</a> 中的短语“苦难的绳索”（“cords of affliction”，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> ；比较<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:6\">2SA 22:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:5\">PSA 18:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:5\">PSA 18:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:3\">PSA 116:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:61\">PSA 119:61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:4\">PSA 129:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:4\">HOS 11:4</a> 中的类似表达）听起来很奇怪，在英文中也是很奇怪的表达。翻译者应该采用功能对等的译词；例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:8\">JOB 36:8</a> b译作“为他们所做的事而受苦”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 保留了绳子的比喻，同时采用了英文的惯用语：“or if trouble, like ropes, ties them up”（直译：“或者，如果苦难像绳索一样捆绑住他们”）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:27\">PSA 118:27</a> 的希伯来文本意思不确定。大多数英文译本（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ），以及《〈诗篇〉手册》（<em>A Handbook on Psalms</em> ），将<em>‘avoth</em> 一词解作叶子茂盛的树枝，也许与住棚节时的一个习俗有关。有些译本（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Standard Bible\">NASB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New King James Version (1982)\">NKJV</abbr> ）和拉比解经家认为，这个词指的是把祭牲绑到祭坛上的粗绳。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:32\">ACT 27:32</a> 中提到的绳索显然是相当粗的，然而<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:15\">JHN 2:15</a> 所记耶稣在驱赶牲畜和商人离开圣殿时所做的鞭子，可能是由结实的带子做成。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:40\">ACT 27:40</a> ，希腊文<em>zeuktēria</em> 指的是连接船的两个舵桨的绳子（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">8.1.8 舵桨、船舵(steering oar, rudder)&lt;REALIA:8.1.8&gt;</a> 中的插图）。在大多数语言中，翻译者只需要使用一个表示“绳子”的词语。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
